name: Libertarian Auction House
description: Launch of the Libertarian Auction House of Non Fungible Tokens related to art and digital assets in the Tezos blockchain. Mind-blowing ideas will appear into your life while being part of this auction house, you will have conversations with people from different cultures and different backgrounds. It is a great opportunity to open your mind, grow as an individual and to expand the horizons of your life. An exceptional place for networking, expand the capabilities of your business and the access to new markets.
